{"tid":994720,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[未出發，先精緊]同屋企人旅行大家會點plan？","createTime":"2019-01-25T02:03:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-25T03:48:24.000Z","uid":47741,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7ec6a4d455c4021675b54679bfe271c49f0a4e1e","tid":994720,"uid":47741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T02:03:45.000Z","msg":"話說今年內會同屋企人去東京旅行，咁我識日文而屋企人又草根既情況下自然乜都要我準備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但經歷過以前既教訓，plan果陣你話同佢地傾佢地又會講你話事得架啦<br />\n但最後又會話「點解成日係咁行路架」「我想睇多d大自然喎」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後諗諗下，其實自己plan完去到又係做導遊咁都唔撚係旅行黎既<br />\n而家諗緊好唔好去報下日本人都會去果d bus tour之類一日或者兩日遊咁<br />\n橫掂上一輩都係旅行團style岩佢地多d<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.club-t.com/bus/chiba/?link_id=cMaN\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.club-t.com%2Fbus%2Fchiba%2F%3Flink_id%3DcMaN&d=7Gg4yc1GkjEDi0YnFurNPW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=73096921\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.club-t.com/bus/chiba/?link_id=cMaN</a><br />\n係呢個網搵左搵，即日回來大概1萬yen以上，訓一晚既平均2萬yen以上一個人<br />\n一家四口即一日要使多4萬起碼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住問一個英文幾勁既日本朋友意見，佢好似做緊part time導遊<br />\n介紹左個網黎話佢有係呢間公司接單 <br />\n<a href=\"https://otomo-inc.com/zh-TW/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fotomo-inc.com%2Fzh-TW%2F&d=7Gg4yc1GkjEDi0YnFurNPW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=2816ea77\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://otomo-inc.com/zh-TW/</a><br />\n望落個網靚靚仔仔同埋價錢尚算合理，可能bus tour同呢個都試下伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋重點係有中文導遊就唔使我乜q都翻譯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n去6日5夜仲有時間試其他方法，大家仲有冇咩好橋集思廣益？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61875f69197911d2661ad51182288c14f26a93a5","tid":994720,"uid":116530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T02:05:15.000Z","msg":"打手？"},{"pid":"ca462cfe3e0a8c5f98f9dea064b636646a91212d","tid":994720,"uid":100143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"61875f69197911d2661ad51182288c14f26a93a5","tid":994720,"uid":116530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T02:05:15.000Z","msg":"打手？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T02:06:50.000Z","msg":"打手"},{"pid":"7a58da04ebaa71f8e24b71ccd5a6afa39e23de7f","tid":994720,"uid":201374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T02:28:58.000Z","msg":"精乜撚緊，精緊咪射囉"},{"pid":"8c23413d7286edc4f9fbc1f49b77c7f937b40cc8","tid":994720,"uid":28972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a58da04ebaa71f8e24b71ccd5a6afa39e23de7f","tid":994720,"uid":201374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T02:28:58.000Z","msg":"精乜撚緊，精緊咪射囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T02:44:20.000Z","msg":"打多幾個字都懶好on9<br />\n利申唔知佢想講乜"},{"pid":"ebcefb7988426b39c17714f24f3ebc195b03b41c","tid":994720,"uid":6833,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T03:42:15.000Z","msg":"係香港跟旅行團算啦"},{"pid":"9332fea70c628d557f78195b91f127eea80ff869","tid":994720,"uid":157579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ebcefb7988426b39c17714f24f3ebc195b03b41c","tid":994720,"uid":6833,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T03:42:15.000Z","msg":"係香港跟旅行團算啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T03:44:58.000Z","msg":"咪係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e41f1c81b3a317c95c4651b70d248461aa4c469","tid":994720,"uid":91813,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T03:48:24.000Z","msg":"jetour 勝景遊 翠明<br />\n唔好自己搞"}]}